      • create

        public antlr.collections.AST create(antlr.Token token,
                                    java.lang.String s)
        Override Antlr's default use of the class name and reflection. Antlrs's call to its createUsingCtor() looks a bit expensive to me. Here, we're able to just use a switch on the token type, because that will always tell us which subclass to use. We're unlikely to ever want multiple node subclasses for any one token type.
        Overrides:
        create in class antlr.ASTFactory
        Parameters:
        s - Class name... is ignored here, but it is used in the generated parser code for casting the return.
